---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Inbox Agent Pilot - SmolOps"
  description="We're building an AI inbox agent that drafts replies and organizes your messages so you can stop spending evenings on email. Join our free pilot."
>

<!-- Nav -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="container nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
      <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="SmolOps" height="44" />
    </a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#what-it-does">What It Does</a>
      <a href="#use-cases">Use Cases</a>
      <a href="#pilot">The Pilot</a>
      <a href="#signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Join the Free Pilot</a>
    </div>
    <button class="mobile-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu" id="mobile-toggle">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="mobile-menu" id="mobile-menu">
  <a href="#what-it-does">What It Does</a>
  <a href="#use-cases">Use Cases</a>
  <a href="#pilot">The Pilot</a>
  <a href="#signup" class="btn btn-primary">Join the Free Pilot</a>
</div>

<main>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-image"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="section-label">Inbox Agent Pilot</span>
        <h1>Stop spending evenings catching up on customer emails.</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          We're building an AI agent that reads your incoming messages, drafts replies,
          and keeps your inbox organized. You review everything before it goes out.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#signup" class="btn btn-primary">Join the Free Pilot</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M16.67 5L7.5 14.17 3.33 10" stroke="#b8e6c8" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span>No software to install</span>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M16.67 5L7.5 14.17 3.33 10" stroke="#b8e6c8" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span>You stay in control of every reply</span>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M16.67 5L7.5 14.17 3.33 10" stroke="#b8e6c8" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span>Free during the pilot</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Does -->
  <section id="what-it-does" class="what-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="section-label">The Problem</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">You already know what to say. You just don't have time to say it.</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Quote requests, scheduling questions, customer updates, document requests.
          It's the same kinds of messages over and over. You know the answers, but writing them all out every day takes hours.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-grid">
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Reads your messages</h3>
          <p>The agent goes through your inbox and figures out what each customer is asking for.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Drafts replies</h3>
          <p>It writes a reply for you. You can edit it, send it as-is, or toss it. Nothing goes out without you saying so.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Organizes your inbox</h3>
          <p>Important stuff floats to the top. No more digging through your inbox to find the message that actually needs attention right now.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section id="use-cases" class="cases-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="section-label">Use Cases</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">The kinds of messages you deal with every day.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="cases-grid">
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Quote Requests</h3>
          <p>Someone asks "how much for..." and a draft reply with your pricing info is ready to go.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Scheduling Questions</h3>
          <p>"Are you available Thursday?" Instead of three emails back and forth, the agent drafts a clear answer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Customer Updates</h3>
          <p>Job confirmations, status updates, follow-ups. The stuff you know you should send but never get around to.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Common Questions</h3>
          <p>"Do you serve my area?" "What are your hours?" The questions you answer ten times a week, handled for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pilot Explanation -->
  <section id="pilot" class="pilot-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="pilot-grid">
        <div class="pilot-text">
          <span class="section-label">The Pilot Program</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">We want to work with a handful of businesses to get this right.</h2>
          <p>
            This is early. We're not trying to sign up thousands of people. We want to work closely
            with a small group, learn how your business actually runs, and make something that genuinely helps.
          </p>
          <p>Here's what that looks like:</p>
          <ul class="pilot-list">
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M16.67 5L7.5 14.17 3.33 10" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              We'll track how much time the agent actually saves you each week
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M16.67 5L7.5 14.17 3.33 10" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              We'll learn your workflows and tailor the agent to how you work
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M16.67 5L7.5 14.17 3.33 10" stroke="#1c7237" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              Short check-ins so the agent keeps getting better for your business
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pilot-details">
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h3>Completely free</h3>
            <p>No cost during the pilot. We're figuring this out together.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h3>Limited spots</h3>
            <p>We're keeping this small on purpose so we can give each business real attention.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h3>Quick intro call</h3>
            <p>After you sign up, we'll hop on a short call to learn about your business and how you handle messages today.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy -->
  <section class="privacy-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="privacy-content text-center">
        <span class="section-label">Privacy & Trust</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Your emails stay yours.</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin: 0 auto 40px;">
          We know this is sensitive. Here's how we handle it.
        </p>
        <div class="privacy-grid">
          <div class="privacy-item">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
            <h3>Nothing to install</h3>
            <p>It works with the email you already use. No apps, no downloads, no setup on your end.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="privacy-item">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
            <h3>Read and draft only</h3>
            <p>The agent can read messages and write drafts. It can't send anything on your behalf without you approving it first.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="privacy-item">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
            <h3>Your emails stay put</h3>
            <p>Nothing gets moved, copied, or stored somewhere else. Your messages stay right where they are.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="privacy-item">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><line x1="23" y1="11" x2="17" y2="11"/></svg>
            <h3>No one reads your email</h3>
            <p>No human ever sees your messages. The AI handles everything privately and automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ideal Businesses -->
  <section class="ideal-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="section-label">Is This For You?</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">If your business runs on customer messages, this is for you.</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin: 0 auto 40px;">
        You don't need to be tech-savvy. If you spend a chunk of your week answering emails, we can probably help.
      </p>
      <div class="ideal-grid">
        <div class="ideal-item">Landscapers</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">Contractors</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">Cleaning Services</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">Pool Service</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">Salons & Spas</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">Small Retail</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">HVAC & Plumbing</div>
        <div class="ideal-item">Property Managers</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Signup Form -->
  <section id="signup" class="signup-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="section-label">Join the Pilot</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Interested? Tell us about your business.</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin: 0 auto 40px;">
          Fill this out and we'll reach out to set up a quick intro call. No pressure, just a conversation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="form-container">
        <form id="pilot-form" method="POST" action="/api/pilot-signup">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Your name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Jane Smith" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="business_name">Business name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="business_name" name="business_name" required placeholder="Smith's Landscaping" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email address *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="jane@smithslandscaping.com" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone (optional)</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(555) 123-4567" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="business_type">What type of business do you run? *</label>
            <select id="business_type" name="business_type" required>
              <option value="">Select your business type...</option>
              <option value="Landscaping">Landscaping</option>
              <option value="General Contractor">General Contractor</option>
              <option value="Cleaning Service">Cleaning Service</option>
              <option value="Pool Service">Pool Service</option>
              <option value="Salon / Spa">Salon / Spa</option>
              <option value="HVAC">HVAC</option>
              <option value="Plumbing">Plumbing</option>
              <option value="Electrical">Electrical</option>
              <option value="Property Management">Property Management</option>
              <option value="Pest Control">Pest Control</option>
              <option value="Auto Repair">Auto Repair</option>
              <option value="Small Retail">Small Retail</option>
              <option value="Restaurant / Cafe">Restaurant / Cafe</option>
              <option value="Other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Where do customers reach you? (select all that apply)</label>
            <div class="checkbox-grid">
              <label class="checkbox-card">
                <input type="checkbox" name="message_channels" value="Email" />
                <span class="checkbox-label">Email</span>
              </label>
              <label class="checkbox-card">
                <input type="checkbox" name="message_channels" value="SMS / Text" />
                <span class="checkbox-label">SMS / Text</span>
              </label>
              <label class="checkbox-card">
                <input type="checkbox" name="message_channels" value="Phone" />
                <span class="checkbox-label">Phone</span>
              </label>
              <label class="checkbox-card">
                <input type="checkbox" name="message_channels" value="Website Form" />
                <span class="checkbox-label">Website Form</span>
              </label>
              <label class="checkbox-card">
                <input type="checkbox" name="message_channels" value="Social Media" />
                <span class="checkbox-label">Social Media</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message_volume">How many customer messages do you get per day?</label>
            <select id="message_volume" name="message_volume">
              <option value="">Select...</option>
              <option value="Less than 10">Less than 10</option>
              <option value="10-25">10 to 25</option>
              <option value="25-50">25 to 50</option>
              <option value="50+">50+</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="biggest_pain">What's the most repetitive part of managing your inbox?</label>
            <textarea id="biggest_pain" name="biggest_pain" rows="3" placeholder="e.g. I spend an hour every morning going through emails and responding to the same types of questions..."></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAACn_nDMQAfOtT8ef" data-theme="light"></div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full" id="btn-submit">Join the Pilot</button>

          <div id="form-status" class="form-status"></div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="SmolOps" height="36" />
        <p>AI automation for small business.<br/>No software. No hassle. Just less admin work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">SmolOps Home</a>
        <a href="#what-it-does">What It Does</a>
        <a href="#pilot">The Pilot</a>
        <a href="#signup">Sign Up</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} SmolOps. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Nav (scoped copy for this page) */
  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.08);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 72px;
  }
  .nav-logo img { height: 44px; width: auto; }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--green-dark); }
  .nav-links a.btn-primary { color: var(--cream); }
  .nav-links a.btn-primary:hover { color: var(--cream); }
  .btn-sm { padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 14px; }
  .mobile-toggle {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 8px;
  }
  .mobile-toggle span {
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--green-dark);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .mobile-menu {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    top: 72px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 24px;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    z-index: 99;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }
  .mobile-menu a {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    padding: 8px 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .mobile-toggle { display: flex; }
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 160px 0 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg-image {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('/images/inbox-hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    filter: blur(1.5px);
  }
  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      170deg,
      rgba(8, 32, 15, 0.82) 0%,
      rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.75) 50%,
      rgba(8, 32, 15, 0.85) 100%
    );
  }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .hero .section-label {
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-actions { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 120px 0 72px; }
  }

  /* What It Does */
  .what-section {
    background: var(--white);
  }
  .solution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .solution-card {
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.08);
    background: var(--cream-light);
  }
  .solution-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(28, 114, 55, 0.08);
    color: var(--green-mid);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .solution-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .solution-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solution-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Use Cases */
  .cases-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--cream-light) 100%);
  }
  .cases-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .case-card {
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid rgba(18, 73, 35, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .case-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
  .case-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
